            might need. Reach out to us, and we'll ensure you get the answers
            and guidance you're looking for.
          </p>

          <a target="_blank" href="mailto:expdigitalsolution@gmail.com">
            <div class="block mt-4 mb-4">
              <div class="flex gap-4 items-center text-davyGray mb-4">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-envelope sectionSemiLargeText"></i>
                <p class="underline sectionSemiLargeText">
                  expdigitalsolution@gmail.com
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <a
              target="_blank"
              href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=6285942965516&text=Halo%20Tim%20Exp%20Digital%20Solution,%0A%0ASaya%20ingin%20membuat%20website%20untuk%20usaha%20saya%20dan%20mencari%20bantuan%20profesional.%20Apakah%20Anda%20dapat%20membantu%20saya%20dalam%20proyek%20ini?%0A%0ATerima%20kasih%20atas%20perhatian%20Anda."
            >
              <div class="flex gap-4 items-center text-davyGray">
                <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp sectionSemiLargeText"></i>
                <p class="underline sectionSemiLargeText">+62 859-4296-5516</p>
              </div>
            </a>
          </a>

          <div class="block mt-6">
            <Button
              variant="outline"
              className="outline sectionSemiLargeText"
              >Get Started</Button
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 -order-1 md:order-[0]">
        <div
          class="relative mb-5 md:mb-0"
          data-aos="fade-right"
          data-aos-duration="1000"
        >
          <img
            src="/image-contact.png"
            alt=""
            class="z-1 w-auto max-w-full rounded-lg"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- section-one -->
</Layout>
